  "text": "```yaml\n# .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml\nname: Deploy to Staging\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches:\n      - develop\n\njobs:\n  deploy:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout code\n        uses: actions/checkout@v3\n\n      - name: Setup Node.js\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v3\n        with:\n          node-version: '18'\n          cache: 'npm'\n\n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: npm ci\n\n      - name: Build\n        run: npm run build\n\n      - name: Deploy to Staging Server\n        uses: appleboy/ssh-action@master\n        with:\n          host: ${{ secrets.STAGING_HOST }}\n          username: ${{ secrets.STAGING_USERNAME }}\n          key: ${{ secrets.STAGING_SSH_KEY }}\n          script: |\n            cd /var/www/mycrew-staging\n            git pull origin develop\n            npm ci\n            npm run build\n            pm2 restart mycrew-staging\n```\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \".github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml\",\n    \"content\": \"# .github/workflows/deploy-staging.yml\\nname: Deploy to Staging\\n\\non:\\n  push:\\n    branches:\\n      - develop\\n\\njobs:\\n  deploy:\\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\\n    steps:\\n      - name: Checkout code\\n        uses: actions/checkout@v3\\n\\n      - name: Setup Node.js\\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v3\\n        with:\\n          node-version: '18'\\n          cache: 'npm'\\n\\n      - name: Install dependencies\\n        run: npm ci\\n\\n      - name: Build\\n        run: npm run build\\n\\n      - name: Deploy to Staging Server\\n        uses: appleboy/ssh-action@master\\n        with:\\n          host: ${{ secrets.STAGING_HOST }}\\n          username: ${{ secrets.STAGING_USERNAME }}\\n          key: ${{ secrets.STAGING_SSH_KEY }}\\n          script: |\\n            cd /var/www/mycrew-staging\\n            git pull origin develop\\n            npm ci\\n            npm run build\\n            pm2 restart mycrew-staging\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n<review_request>\n{\n  \"title\": \"Staging 배포 파이프라인 안정성 개선 코드 리뷰 요청\",\n  \"assignee\": \"dev_fullstack\",\n  \"message\": \"배포 파이프라인의 의존성 설치 명령어를 `npm install`에서 `npm ci`로 변경하여 빌드의 일관성과 안정성을 확보했습니다. 변경 사항 검토 후 승인 부탁드립니다.\"\n}\n</review_request>",
